## Follow-Up Questions

- Is this for a specific deal or a general awareness update?
- Should I create a battle card for the sales team?
- Are there specific customer conversations where this competitor has come up?
- Do you want me to set up a recurring competitive watch on this company?
- Should this be shared with the sales engineering team?
